column5: Can't seem to find this line ... I know it's new, but is the lack of availability a function of it not being released fully in Canada yet ... supplier issue?
Saw it at the show at the Shimano booth. Thinner than reg PP. Didn't see it at retailers.
Cabalas in Buffalo had not even heard of it yet, that was last week...
check with pro-j tackle they usually have the new stuff first
I have a spool of 100lb, got it off eBay
